metadata.name: Lake Galore - Olsztyn
metadata.description:
Grab a drink, sit on a beach, tune into the sound of the water... and wash yourself into the Summer Galore!

Inspired by the luxury travels and the highest vibrations of the summer, these series reflect on the most beloved resorts in the world. 

Some of them are very well known - but Adriana also wants to highlight summer spots she has been to and deserve bigger recognition.

The first of the series is the birthcity of Adriana - Olsztyn - a capital of a famous region of thousands of lakes. Adriana growing up witnessed a huge transition of her beautiful hometown, which public beach these days is a lake galore heaven. This NFT is a tribute to her roots and recognition of inner growth, beauty and transition. It can definitely compete with St. Tropez.
